(196,1,'2026-05-22 10:49:51','2026-05-22 10:49:51','AI Systems Portfolio Consultation Summary is a reflective resource for individuals and communities navigating the intersection of technology, ethics, and faith.\nThis document synthesizes key insights from consultation work on AI systems, including:\n• Critical analysis of technological claims and societal impacts\n• Frameworks for discernment in complex information environments\n• Practical reflection prompts for personal and communal engagement\n• Grounded perspectives on data privacy, economic modeling, and media literacy\nDesigned for educators, bloggers, small groups, and anyone seeking thoughtful engagement with emerging technologies.\n📄 Format: PDF | 📏 Size: 66 KB | 🔄 Version: 1.0\n\"The goal is not to have all the answers, but to ask better questions—with humility, curiosity, and hope.\"\nHow to use this resource: Download, print for personal reflection, share with a small group, or embed in a blog post using the shortcode below.','AI Systems Portfolio Consultation Summary-ajsbsd@gmail.com.','AI Systems Portfolio Consultation Summary — A reflective PDF toolkit for navigating technology, ethics, and faith. Free download. 📄 66 KB | v1.0','inherit','open','closed','','ai-systems-portfolio-consultation-summary-ajsbsdgmail-com-2','','','2026-05-22 10:54:17','2026-05-22 10:54:17','',0,'https://ongoingstoriesofmysoul.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/AI-Systems-Portfolio-Consultation-Summary-ajsbsd@gmail.com_.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),
